        "Web source 1"
      ],
      "source": "https://grokipedia.com/page/rio_florida"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "Redevelopment plans since 2001 aim to upgrade sewer, water, and roads while preserving Rio’s historic feel.",
